{"tid":1343413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理性少少，唔好再話元朗單野係轉移視線","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:33:55.000Z","uid":264683,"like":189,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ecaa02ba482c1109b4bc7c70554f2fe751cf5f09","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:43:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全部發生事都係有關連架</span><br />\n<br />\n追究黑警濫暴，選擇性執法同追究元朗黑幫暴徒 <br />\n兩單野係冇牴觸架<br />\n係可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時</span></span>進行架<br />\n佢地係一team架<br />\n<br />\n事實上我地可以借力，用黑幫反咬黑警<br />\n我地必須強烈譴責警方喺元朗單野不但冇執法，冇用最低武力制止真。暴徒暴動，導止無辜小市民被無故打傷，記者遭毆打至頭破血流，第四權受嚴重打壓。事後黑警重要舉紅旗掩護班黑幫離開。<br />\n<br />\n文宣，輿論上，必須將黑警同黑幫兩者緊緊相扣<br />\n做到大眾第一印象黑幫=黑警，黑警=黑幫<br />\n知法犯法，黑黑相衛<br />\n叫人再點將香港治安交比班黑警<br />\n要令<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警形象永不反身</span></span><br />\n<br />\n計埋今日港島黑警又開槍又tear gas又見人就打<br />\n更加印證港共政府草菅人命<br />\n為政治目的，不惜動用黑幫，授權警察濫暴濫權<br />\n傷及無辜市民，記者，議員，社工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府要負最大責任[</span>/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n一定一定要將矛頭指返去政府<br />\n重申五大訴求之餘，<br />\n更要強調<br />\n係政府嘅[size=5]<span style=\"color: gold;\">無能</span></span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">危機處理失當</span></span>，先會引發而家咁嘅亂局<br />\n<br />\n總之我地大把黑材料大做文章<br />\n<br />\n而睇返我地今日，整爆一兩塊玻璃，幫鄰國國徽做下藝術工程，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Wfc?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n<br />\n保持頭腦清晰之餘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仇就一定要報</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dc9a41d8c81751c7a276c4ec59236c76c25100","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲呀今次"},{"pid":"fc7ad00c4f993ef319c831c44a57159cb5c291ac","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6ab4bae9aeb8bb708cadfb5cb8f9a96e14d8bc","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑黑相衛可恥"},{"pid":"9c9ef066922c5318c5aa62ae6830ae4dc51cd815","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0718d529b45472b8a888017b8aedc5b246cc1a","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdd398cde11f8d4280c2548d9fc02424deb431b","tid":1343413,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:02:32.000Z","msg":"元朗中環 兩邊都重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1a2af29870d4596422edc3d0412024e8bd463a","tid":1343413,"uid":276956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:38.000Z","msg":"竟然有人用「英文」做反宣傳！<br />\n721 HK yuan long people in black, legislative Lam as.well, were beaten/721 香港元朗白衣人暴打黑衣人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpIwj_X6Ieg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlpIwj_X6Ieg&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXciC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=d4a7aab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpIwj_X6Ieg</a><br />\n<br />\n一定要向全世界做「反反宣傳」，讓林鄭政府和中共柒出國際。"},{"pid":"908f50f9214742d6be8b93f3e6e15d78b52230f6","tid":1343413,"uid"