 red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同時進行 兩邊都推<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n對準政權，清算黑警！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9467459f2b46e306b6b183a0e00b313a71db4629","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"元朗警區指揮官游乃強：<br />\n刑事同事落到嚟係見唔到有任何揸攻擊性武器<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得救"},{"pid":"59509b6ccbbaa11208b5f34f8718cd8fa4bfeb80","tid":1343413,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08d8bf6f55db4995ab9a9b6c88ee02be43aa6856","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fc6bfa21025654460de7f418f7eb72e8877c19","tid":1343413,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecaa02ba482c1109b4bc7c70554f2fe751cf5f09","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:43:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全部發生事都係有關連架</span><br />\n<br />\n追究黑警濫暴，選擇性執法同追究元朗黑幫暴徒 <br />\n兩單野係冇牴觸架<br />\n係可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時</span></span>進行架<br />\n佢地係一team架<br />\n<br />\n事實上我地可以借力，用黑幫反咬黑警<br />\n我地必須強烈譴責警方喺元朗單野不但冇執法，冇用最低武力制止真。暴徒暴動，導止無辜小市民被無故打傷，記者遭毆打至頭破血流，第四權受嚴重打壓。事後黑警重要舉紅旗掩護班黑幫離開。<br />\n<br />\n文宣，輿論上，必須將黑警同黑幫兩者緊緊相扣<br />\n做到大眾第一印象黑幫=黑警，黑警=黑幫<br />\n知法犯法，黑黑相衛<br />\n叫人再點將香港治安交比班黑警<br />\n要令<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警形象永不反身</span></span><br />\n<br />\n計埋今日港島黑警又開槍又tear gas又見人就打<br />\n更加印證港共政府草菅人命<br />\n為政治目的，不惜動用黑幫，授權警察濫暴濫權<br />\n傷及無辜市民，記者，議員，社工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府要負最大責任[</span>/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n一定一定要將矛頭指返去政府<br />\n重申五大訴求之餘，<br />\n更要強調<br />\n係政府嘅[size=5]<span style=\"color: gold;\">無能</span></span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">危機處理失當</span></span>，先會引發而家咁嘅亂局<br />\n<br />\n總之我地大把黑材料大做文章<br />\n<br />\n而睇返我地今日，整爆一兩塊玻璃，幫鄰國國徽做下藝術工程，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Wfc?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n<br />\n保持頭腦清晰之餘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仇就一定要報</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"1673c2f77c59a595252cb52fd326affe41a427f0","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7f0ec00f3e6ec7858671ee279e2579d113a99c","tid":1343413,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}